name: Gehirn-Analyse 2
overview: A German language, mixed challenge game with wordsearch and a simple quiz game for one to four players created by Hannes Malecki of Welle Erdball and released as part of the mixed Competition at Willow Party 2005 where it came in second place, it comes with some very nice music. It was also released in GO64! 2005/08. This game is the second part in a trilogy of games.
